{Speech 3}{}{Время:60000 Нет ответа:Завершить диалог / Close dialog}
{Speech 4}{}{Nancy? And who are you to talk to me?}
{Speech 4 Answer 5}{}{Come on, would it hurt you to answer? @sex@|Pal|Honey| I'm a friend of hers}
{Speech 5}{}{I've never heard Nancy talk about you. Get lost! I'll tell Sid everything! He'll beat you up!}
{Speech 5 Answer 6}{}{Don't get worked up.@@Come on, take it easy...@@Why are you all so jumpy...}
{Speech 6}{}{Well, who doesn't know cute little Nancy. What about her? Did she OD? [Giggles]}
{Speech 6 Answer 7}{}{Yeah, I'm wondering myself what happened to her. No one's seen her for two weeks now... I want to find the girl.}
{Speech 7}{}{I doubt I can help you. I'm not really friends with her. She and Sid are too reckless. Better to keep your distance from such people.}
